    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ECHOING SILENCE</strong><br> is an atmospheric exploration experience set inside a cave that feels alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no monsters chasing you and no cheap jump scares. The fear comes from the place itself. From doubt. From the weight of silence. From corridors that look the same until you start questioning whether you’re moving forward or looping back., treacherous terrain makes every step a tense, deliberate choice — where a single mistake could mean the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore. Observe. Survive.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/965cfca02ab1133638029333149195cc.poster.avif?t=1765251261\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/965cfca02ab1133638029333149195cc.webm?t=1765251261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/965cfca02ab1133638029333149195cc.mp4?t=1765251261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You enter the tunnels to uncover what lies beyond the reach of light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And slowly realize the greatest threat isn’t what’s hiding in the dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s what the environment does to your mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/fad3ed5d96ecafb4fb5d14ced6dbbf3b.poster.avif?t=1765251261\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/fad3ed5d96ecafb4fb5d14ced6dbbf3b.webm?t=1765251261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/fad3ed5d96ecafb4fb5d14ced6dbbf3b.mp4?t=1765251261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Environmental and psychological horror</strong> without relying on monsters or cheap jump scares.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Similar-looking tunnels and passages</strong> inspired by real underground disorientation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slow-burn exploration</strong> focused on atmosphere and environmental storytelling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discoveries and decisions</strong> that shape your understanding of what happened.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings</strong> based on what you uncover and how you proceed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Light survival mechanics</strong> to reinforce urgency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/65bfe13c531e77e42ddeb7a7970dabfd.poster.avif?t=1765251261\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/65bfe13c531e77e42ddeb7a7970dabfd.webm?t=1765251261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151230/extras/65bfe13c531e77e42ddeb7a7970dabfd.mp4?t=1765251261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Please note</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’re looking for combat, high-octane action, or classic puzzle-driven progression, this may not be your game.<br>But if you want an immersive, unsettling, contemplative descent, <strong>Echoing Silence</strong> is here to swallow your sense of direction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add <strong>Echoing Silence</strong> to your wishlist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do you have the courage to face the darkness… and the silence?</strong></p>",
